Class Unsatisfiable

java.lang.Object

java.lang.Exception
Datastructures.Results.Result
Datastructures.Results.Unsatisfiable
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
UnsatInputClause, UnsatisfiableClause, UnsatisfiableInterval, UnsatisfiableLiteral
public abstract class Unsatisfiable extends Result
This class represents the final reason for an unsatisfiability in the clauses. It must be subclassed for representing more specific reasons for the unsatisfiability.
